value.body:
Hopefully there will be no double voting problems, let's see. 

@Steemvoter wrote that there could be a problem with low voting power and at the same time low steem power, let's see.

@better is cool. Always more reward after I got featured.

@Robotev is a friendly communicating bot and somehow votes like I vote, I would have to check again, but it's all a bit much now. My plan: Hope that nothing will break :-D

Street promo goes as usual. Many people a day make photos of the hat and the logo. Good mix of ~ 50 people a day.

Among the people today was a manager of a 'club of the year' from The Middle East. 2500 people party on the rooftop, daily. Now they will make a new one somewhere else. Rocknroll..

I hear people are flocking into the city slowly. Maybe we'll meet and you can see me in action.

I will check if the voting power goes up, otherwise pause everything until it's full again.


@craig-grant makes good vids and I got  
the info about steemvoter from him.

http://tinyimg.io/i/FyvKoBf.jpg

A tourist from Mexico gave me a cigarette with a nice package. It's romantic compared to Marlboro and others.

Thanks for your support. Big thanks to the witnesses.
